    "\n",
    "Main options for \"1 MeV H in Fe\" example:\n",
    "- Ion beam: 1 MeV H$^+$ (default - no change needed)\n",
    "- Target material: Fe (default - no change needed) \n",
    "- Target size: 10 μm square\n",
    "- Flight path: \"Variable\" (for max efficiency)"
   ]
